  ('dietitian-moex-08167', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-099-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '細胞是以下列何種方式產生前列腺素（prostaglandins）？', '["以RNA作為模板經轉譯作用（translation）而產生", "在高基氏體（Golgi apparatus）中以醣類作為原料而產生", "以甲硫胺酸（methionine）作為原料經一系列的反應而產生", "以多元不飽和脂肪酸（ ）作為原料經一系列的反應而產生 polyunsaturated fatty acids"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "880e9dd22e13", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "109", "s": "100", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
